    <releaseNotes>'Merged PR 10886: Report engineering DLL version in console and ituff'
'Merged PR 10880: Update pVal tool to fix part of pipeline unstable issues'
'Merged PR 10493: Prime 13 PrimeSDK'
'Merged PR 10732: [MTT] MultiTrialTest test destroy and recreate feature support.'
'Merged PR 10498: Bug fix for TOS4 TestMethodBase not gracefully returning to kernel scope'
'Merged PR 9972: enable simba sdj  on 13.xx.xx'
'Merged PR 9983: Updated PrimeKernel to get a better error message if Prime load fails on TOS3'</releaseNotes>
